<h1 id=3D"the-spin-lock-that-burned-cpus">The spin-lock that burned CPUs</h=
1>
<p>You may have realized that our spin-lock will=E2=80=A6 spin doing nothin=
g, the loop is empty.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>=F0=9F=A4=AA =E2=80=9CGreat, it=E2=80=99ll attempt to take ownership fas=
